{"tid":1660562,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[國際戰線]入黎令制裁法案遍地開花","createTime":"2019-10-17T14:36:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T12:57:08.000Z","uid":63045,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d4811c37af51db9ae0ec6cafa067cbdc456a641e","tid":1660562,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T14:36:26.000Z","msg":"香港眾志未來兩年國際遊說工作，主要有四大工作範籌，包括：<br />\n<br />\n📌確保《香港人權民主法案》在美國國會通過及切實執行<br />\n📌推動全球各國通過《香港人權民主法案》或類似制裁機制<br />\n📌在英國、美國、台灣、日本、德國設立當地港人遊說網絡<br />\n📌在國際層面支援港人商業抵制行動<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHKIAD 同眾志都好努力做緊野，大家一齊比啲支持佢地，香港人乜都唔多，錢最多，捐爆佢地！！<br />\n<br />\n香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃 Hong Kong IAD Crowdfunding Plan<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaASrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=a9c0ee4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港眾志國際眾籌計劃<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/香港眾志國際眾籌計劃-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaASrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=58dcdebf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/香港眾志國際眾籌計劃-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project</a>"},{"pid":"0b34416426a38c67b408b54b25f1d3f3614c22ba","tid":1660562,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T14:36:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/afoWPNY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FafoWPNY.jpg&h=041452ea&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"04b50b2eafb3ec79740f5875a2055d1ca15ff9b1","tid":1660562,"uid":325269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201